{"tid":1040741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚買中國人壽 咪撚買中國人壽 咪撚買中國人壽","createTime":"2019-02-28T10:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T14:15:45.000Z","uid":167330,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1b351bac86d3951eb32117359f89259290589733","tid":1040741,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:08:34.000Z","msg":"呢間閪公司會諗盡辦法拖延claim 保險<br />\n<br />\n話說小弟有兩份人壽保險，連登仔一定會話個腦正常都唔會買支那野，但兩份野係老母幫我買，我有得揀一定唔會買<br />\n<br />\n話說小弟一份保險係5年前買，另一份係大概10個月前買，而好不幸地，我居然喺第二份保險生效咗一個月之後就因為心率不正入咗醫院，而之後亦都因為呢個問題入過幾次。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於時間上好敏感，佢哋就當咗我係呃保險咁，翻查我過往嘅求診記錄。然後佢哋發現喺我買第二份保險之前，有去醫院求診過，但我嗰陣只係因為啲感冒頭痛去睇醫生。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋又話翻查記錄話我有病史（包括手腳麻痺、大腿有淋巴結節等等，但最後冇事，醫生亦check過冇問題），但佢哋話我有誠信問題，認為我有隱瞞病史。（但試問連醫生都證明冇問題，即係冇病啦，冇病又點隱暪病歷呀？我當時只係擔心有問題順便叫醫生check下，係有啲疑病嘅心態）<br />\n<br />\n我當我買第二份保險嘅時間敏感，當我呃保險我可以理解，但佢哋連我第一份保險（五年前買）都拖，5年前冇病歷喇掛？但而家佢拖咗半年都未肯claim返錢畀我<br />\n<br />\n總之，各位咪撚買中國人壽，支那野冇樣野係好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2feb92de7a49f5fab1d55e5a03dd666d349e4e","tid":1040741,"uid":140234,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:11:34.000Z","msg":"係 好撚閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af5fb15376190ba16d8183727ba872a2cf11835","tid":1040741,"uid":167330,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:11:43.000Z","msg":"雖然喺買第二份保險前已經有淋巴結節，但係正常人都會摸到，我嗰陣唔了解以為有問題，後尾先會叫醫生check，check過係正常size，即係冇病，點可以當我隱瞞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0ed55522edacd7e275cfac6f97696305268da6","tid":1040741,"uid":12612,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:12:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"394da6f720bd9699af5731a6dc3ae0f772283660","tid":1040741,"uid":193290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:13:27.000Z","msg":"買左2628點算?"},{"pid":"bf91cd27d804d3f5f2890b2160b607f14b41170e","tid":1040741,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"5e0ed55522edacd7e275cfac6f97696305268da6","tid":1040741,"uid":12612,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:12:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:22:17.000Z","msg":"衰在冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n病歷包括鼻敏感（agent話唔計）、頭痛睇醫生（應該係感冒、大腿淋巴買嗰陣好似有（但嗰陣冇察覺，但我知道係正常野冇理佢，之後只係抱住順便check下嘅心態去check清楚，事實證明真係正常野。<br />\n<br />\n個情況就好似你本來一直都有粒睪丸，之後去開睇醫生順便問清楚有睪丸係咪正常咁<br />\n<br />\n我發誓我有心呃保險就爛jj"},{"pid":"7936aaa86d4d5532975ee9c678834e828d7c5070","tid":1040741,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:22:54.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"cb8d641eb0d27ea3d383f1513944c068eb8f556a","tid":1040741,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"394da6f720bd9699af5731a6dc3ae0f772283660","tid":1040741,"uid":193290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:13:27.000Z","msg":"買左2628點算?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b131d2647365f02a56d9f21c3bfd16470bf536c","tid":1040741,"uid":76310,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:24:46.000Z","msg":"傻閪<br />\n<br />\n中淫獸係強国出名無得賠<br />\n佢地連蝗民都呃, 你班港豬仲幫襯, 抵撚死"},{"pid":"cecfa6f57d579372a1694973b0820816c24b7021","tid":1040741,"uid":76310,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:30:58.000Z","msg":"抵撚你死<br />\n<br />\n中国野都買, 淨係比錢, 一毫子都無得賠<br />\n<br />\n你叫佢賠, 等同叫国家比錢, 你諗下得唔得"},{"pid":"e4068370de0d7831c0caf6a9b75ba8fb785b176f","tid":1040741,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:31:38.000Z","msg":"啱啱問過老母份保險嘅生效日期，連淋巴結節都係買咗保險之後先留意到有，即係買之前係絕對健康<br />\n<br />\n但佢而家老屈話係買保險前已經有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲話係向醫院拎返嚟嘅記錄，明明買之前冇野"},{"pid":"9530131165ebf130bbe91892357e65e99c0827b9","tid":1040741,"uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:32:41.000Z","msg":"正路應該保監會投訴？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ia.org.hk/tc/aboutus/lodge_a_complaint.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ia.org.hk%2Ftc%2Faboutus%2Flodge_a_complaint.html&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=6688354b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ia.org.hk/tc/aboutus/lodge_a_complaint.html</a>"},{"pid":"49522d2f6d14707032ba2904fb2a7b771e57e983","tid":1040741,"uid":76310,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:32:50.000Z","msg":"中国人寿保险公司是不是骗子公司？我的理赔他们找理由拒赔<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/p/1942332382\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F1942332382&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=2787b951\" target=\"_blank\">http://tieba.baidu.com/p/1942332382</a><br />\n<br />\n佢強国人都唔賠, 你算係乜<br />\n抵撚死"},{"pid":"6fd1b1b1f3370fe67e47fcdf5194c205dc673c3a","tid":1040741,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9530131165ebf130bbe91892357e65e99c0827b9","tid":1040741,"uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:32:41.000Z","msg":"正路應該保監會投訴？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ia.org.hk/tc/aboutus/lodge_a_complaint.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ia.org.hk%2Ftc%2Faboutus%2Flodge_a_complaint.html&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=6688354b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ia.org.hk/tc/aboutus/lodge_a_complaint.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:33:31.000Z","msg":"你向国企投訴? 即係向皇帝告御狀, 想死?"},{"pid":"9b044f0964afd9a583d3f3800c40da85af86c56a","tid":1040741,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fd1b1b1f3370fe67e47fcdf5194c205dc673c3a","tid":1040741,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9530131165ebf130bbe91892